hadiths[55]{hadithnumber,text}:
4159,Saiyedna Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kanghi karney se mana farmaya hai siwaye iskey ke eik din chhod kar ho.
4160,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke as-haab mein se eik aadmi Hazrat Fazaala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaya jabkey wo Misr mein (ameer) they. wahan pahunchey to un se kaha : main tumhen bilaa wajah milney nahin aaya hun balke maine aur tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se eik hadees suni thi , mujhey umeed hai ke wo tumhen khoob yaad hogi . unhoney kaha : kon si hadees ? farmaya : falan falan ! phir kaha : aur kya wajeh hai ke main tumhen paraa ganda sar (bikhre hue sir) dekh raha hun halanke tum is ilaqey ke ameer ho? Hazrat Fazaala (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tehqiq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein bahut ziyada asbabe-aesh jama kerney aur bahut ziyada zeb aur zeenat se mana farmaya kartey they. phir puchha : kya wajeh hai ke tumharey jootey nahin hain? kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein hukm farmaya kartey they ke kabhi kabhi nangey paon bhi raha karen."
4161,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ne eik din aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney duniya ka (asbabe-aesh (samane-aesh) aur daulat ka ( zikr kiya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum suntey nahin ho? kya tum suntey nahin ho? bila-shuba sadgi emaan ka hissa hai, bila-shuba sadgi emaan ka hissa hai.'' yani zeb aur zeenat aur aesho daulat ko chhod dena. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne raawi hadees ke mutalliq kaha ke ye Abu-Umama bin Solba Ansari hain. (Raziallahu anhu)"
4162,Saiyedna Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik khas murakkab khushbu thi aap is se khushbu lagaya kartey they.
4163,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney baal rakhey hon to chahiye ke unhen bana sanwaar kar rakhey.''"
4164,"Kareema binte Hammam bayan karti hain ke eik aurat ne Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se mehndi ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney jawab diya : is mein koi harj nahin lekin main usey napasand karti hun, kyonkey merey Habib (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko uski boo napasand thi. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke us aurat ka maqsad sar ke baalon ko mehndi lagana tha."
4165,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Hind dukhtar Utba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! mujh se baiat ley lijiye ! aapney farmaya : ''main us waqt tak tumhari baiat nahin lun ga jab tak ke tum apni hatheliyon ko rang na lo , ye to goya darindey ki hatheliyan hain.''"
4166,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik aurat ne pardey ke peechhey se apney haath se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf ishara kiya, uskey paas aap ke liye eik khat tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna haath khinch liya aur farmaya : ''mujhey nahin maloom ke ye haath mard ka hai ya aurat ka?'' usney kaha : aurat ka , aapney farmaya : ''agar to aurat hoti to apney naakhunon ko rang leti .'' yani mehndi lagaati."
4167,Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Ameer Muawiya bin Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anhu) se suna jis saal ke unhoney hajj kiya. unhoney member par se apney muhafiz ke haath se baalon ka eik guchchhaa pakda aur kaha : aey ehale-Madina ! tumharey ulama kahan hain? maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai ke aap is tarah ki chizon se mana farmatey they. aapney farmaya : ''bani Israel tabhi halak huey jab unki aurton ne inka istimal shuru kar diya.''
4168,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne lanat farmaee hai us aurat par jo kisi ke baalon mein baal jodey aur us aurat par jo ye kaam karwaaey , aur us aurat par jo jism goodey aur us par jo apna jism gudwaaey."
4169,"(Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne ba-waaste Muhammad bin Esa aur Usman bin Abi Sheba riwayat kiya) Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ''lanat ki hai Allah ne un aurton par jo jism godein aur gudwaayen.''  Muhammad bin Esa ne kaha : aur jo baal jod kar lambey karen. Usman ne kaha : aur jo chehrey ke baal ukheden . . . phir dono shaikh riwayat mein muttafiq hain. . . aur jo Husn ki khatir daanton mein khala (gap) karwaaen, Allah ki khilqat (banawat) ko tabdeel karen. ye baat banu-Asad ki eik aurat ko pahunchi jisey Umme-Yaqoob kaha jata tha. Usman ne ye izafa bayan kiya : aur usney pura Quran padh rakha tha. . . phir dono shaikh riwayat mein muttafiq hain. . . wo khatoon Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood ke paas aai aur kaha : mujhey aap se ye baat pahunchi hai ke aapney un aurton par lanat ki hai jo jism godein aur gudwaaeyn. Muhammad ne kaha : aur jo baal jod kar lambey karen. aur Usman ne kaha : aur jo chehrey ke baal ukheden . phir dono riwayat mein muttafiq hain. aur jo daanton mein khala (gap) karwaaen. Usman ne kaha : zeenat ki khatir , Allah ki khilqat (banawat) ko badalney waliyan hain. to Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mujhey kya hua ke main un par lanat na karun jin par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne lanat ki hai aur ye Allah ki kitab mein bhi waarid hai. wo boli tehqiq maine pura Quran jo do gatton ke darmiyan mein hai padha hai mujhey to us mein ye hukm nahin mila hai, unhoney kaha : Allah ki qasam ! agar to ne padha hota to yaqinan pa leti. phir unhoney ye aayat padhi ({ وَمَا آتَاكُمُ الرَّسُولُ فَخُذُوهُ وَمَا نَهَاكُمْ عَنْهُ فَانْتَهُوا }) ''aur Rasool jo kuchh tumhen dey den wo ley lo aur jis se rok den us se ruk jao.'' aurat ne kaha : main un mein se kaee chizen tumhari biwi par bhi dekhti hun. unhoney kaha : andar jao aur dekh lo. chunanche wo andar gaee aur phir bahir aa gaee . unhoney puchha : kya dekha hai? . . . Usman ne kaha . . . aurat ne kaha : maine kuchh nahin dekha, to Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar ye hota to hamarey sath na hoti."
4170,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke lanat ki gaee hai us aurat par jo baal jodey aur judwaaye , jo chehrey ke baal ukhede aur ukhadwaaye aur jo jism goodey ya gudwaaey baghair kisi bimari ke. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke (واصلہ) se murad wo aurat hai jo dusri aurton ke baal jodti ho aur (مستوصلہ) wo hai jo ye kaam karwaaey. (نامصہ) wo hai jo palkon ke baalon ko nochti aur unhen bareek banati ho aur (متنمصہ) wo hai jo ye kaam karwaaey. (واشمہ) wo hai jo chehrey ki jild par surmey ya siyahi se til waghera banati ho aur (مستوشمہ) wo hai jo ye kaam karwaati ho."
4171,Janab Saeed bin Jubair (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke dhaagon se bani choti (موباف) mein koi harj nahin. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke goya Saeed (Rahimahullah) ki raey ye thi ke bil-khusus aurton ke baal (aur baal laga kar) jodnaa hi mana hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : aur aisey hi Imam Ahmed (Rahimahullah) kehtey they ke dhaagon ki choti ka koi harj nahin hai.
4172,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisey khushbu pesh ki jaey to wo usey wapis na karey. bila-shuba iski mahak umda hoti hai aur is mein koi bojh bhi nahin hota.''"
4173,"Saiyedna Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi aurat khushbu laga kar kisi qaum par se guzarti hai taake wo uski khushbu pa len to wo aisi aur aisi hai.'' aapney badi sakht baat farmaee."
4174,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ko eik aurat mili unhoney us se itr ki khushbu mehsoos ki aur uski chadar ka pallu ghubar bhi udata aa raha tha. unhoney us se kaha : aey Jabbaar ki bandi ! bhala to masjid se aai hai? usney kaha : haan . unhoney kaha : to kya usi ke liye to ne khushbu lagai thi? kehney lagi, haan. unhoney kaha : maine apney mehboob Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai aap farmatey they : ''jo aurat is masjid ke liye khushbu laga kar aaye uski Namaz qubul nahin yahan tak ke wapis jaey aur us ehtimam se ghusl karey jaisey ke wo janabat se karti hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : (إعصار) ka mafhoom hai (ghubar)."
4175,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne riwayat kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis aurat ne khushbu ki dhooni li ho, wo hamarey sath Isha ki Namaz mein shareek na ho. ibne-Nufail ne (عشاء الآخرة) ke lafz riwayat kiye."
4176,"Saiyedna Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke main (safar se wapis aaya aur) raat ko apney ghar walon ke yahan pahuncha jabke merey haath phat chukey they, to unhoney mujhey Zaafran laga di. main subah ke waqt Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur salam arz kiya to aapney mujhey jawab diya na khush-aamadeed kaha balke farmaya : ''jao aur isey apney aap se dho kar aao.'' chunanche main gaya aur usey dho dala aur aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabkey iska kuchh asar aur dagh mujh par baqi reh gaya tha. maine salam pesh kiya to aapney mujhey jawab diya na khush-aamadeed kaha aur farmaya : ''jao aur usey apney aap se dho kar aao.'' chunanche main gaya aur isey (dobara) dho kar hazire-khidmat hua aur salam kaha : to aapney mujhey jawab diya aur khush-aamadeed bhi kaha. aur farmaya : ''bila-shuba farishtey kafir ke janaazey par khair ke sath hazir nahin hotey aur na aisey aadmi ke paas aatey hain jisney Zaafran lagai ho aur na junbi (sambhog ke bad naapaki ki halat mein insan) ke paas aatey hain.'' albatta junbi ke liye rukhsat (chhoot) di ke jab wo sona ya khana peena chahey to wuzu kar ley."
4177,"Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke maine Zaafran lagai , aur mazkura baala qissa bayan kiya. aur pehli hadees ziyada kamil hai. us riwayat mein dhoney ka zikr hai. ibne-Juraij kehtey hain ke maine umr bin Ata se puchha : kya wo us waqt ehram mein they? unhoney kaha : nahin, muqeem (niwasi) they."
4178,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala us aadmi ki Namaz qubul nahin farmata jiskey jism par maamuli si khalooq bhi lagi ho. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain sanad mein waarid Rabeea bin Anas ke naana, dada se murad Zaid aur Ziyad hain."
4179,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai ke mard Zaafran lagaeyn. aur Ismail (bin Ibrahim ( se ye lafz marwi (bayan) hai : (أن يتزعفر الرجل)."
4180,"Saiyedna Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen qism ke logon ke paas farishtey nahin aatey hain. kafir ki laash aur jisney khaluq (Zaafran se murakkab khushbu) lagai ho aur junbi (sambhog ke bad naapaki ki halat mein insan) aadmi , siwaey iske ke wuzu kar ley.''"
4181,"Hazrat Waleed bin Aqba (ibne-Abi Mueet) ne kaha : jab Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Makka Fateh kiya to ehle-Makka apney bachchon ko aap ke paas laney lagey. aap unke liye barkat ki dua farmatey aur unke saron par haath phertey. mujhey bhi aap ke paas laya gaya, magar mujh par khaluq (murakkab Zaafran) lagi thi. to aapney is wajeh se merey sar par haath na phera."
4182,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya jabkey us par zard rang ka nishan tha. aur bahut kam aisey hota ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi par koi naa-pasandida chiz dekhen aur barahe-rast usey kuchh kahen. jab wo chala gaya to aapney farmaya : ''agar tum usey keh do ke apney par se usey dho daley (to bahut behtar ho).''
4183,"Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke maine kabhi nahin dekha ke kisi ne zulfen rakhi hon, surkh joda pehna ho aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se badh kar khoobsurat ho. Muhammad bin Sulaiman ne mazeed kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zulfein kandhon tak aati thin. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Israel ne Abu-Is'haq se riwayat kiya ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baal aap ke kandhon ko chhotey they aur Shoba ne kaha ke kanon ki lauon tak aatey they."
4184,Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne baal rakhey huey they jo aap ke kanon ki lauon tak aatey they.
4185,Saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baal aap ke kanon ki lauon tak aatey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is mein Shoba ko weham hua hai.
4186,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baal aap ke kanon ke darmiyan tak aatey they.
4187,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baal (وفرہ) se zaayda aur (جمہ) se kam hotey they.
4188,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke ehle-kitab apney baalon ko aisey hi sidha (peechhey ki taraf) chhod diya kartey they jabke mushrekin mang nikala kartey they. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jin umur (baton) mein koi hukm na diya gaya hota, aap un mein ehle-kitab ki muwaafiqat karna pasand farmatey they, chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney baal sidhey rakhney shuru kiye magar baad mein mang nikalney lagey."
4189,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baalon mein mang nikalney lagti to aap ke sar ke bechun-beech se nikaalti aur aap ki peshani ke baalon ko aap ki aakhon ke samney latkaati (yani phir unhen aadho-aadh kar deti).
4190,"Hazrat Waael bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to merey baal bahut lambey they, chunanche jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey dekha to farmaney lagey : ''nahusat hai, nahusat hai.'' chunanche main wapis gaya aur unhen kaat dala aur phir agley din hazire-khidmat hua to aapney farmaya : ''maine tujhey koi buri baat nahin kahi thi aur ab ye behtar hai.''"
4191,Sayeda Umme-Haani (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Makka tashrif laye to unke baalon ki chaar laten thin jo goondhee hui thin.
4192,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke (Hazrat Jaafar bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat ke moqe par) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aale-Jaafar ko teen din tak kuchh na kaha, phir unke paas aaye aur farmaya : ''aaj ke baad merey bhai par mat ronaa.'' phir farmaya : ''merey bhatijon ko merey paas bulao.'' isliye hamin laya gaya, goya ham chidiyaa ke bachchey they. (yani hamarey saron ke baal bikhrey huey they) to aapney farmaya : ''merey paas hajjaam ko bulao.'' to aapney us se kaha aur usney hamarey sar moond daley."
4193,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ''qaza' '' se mana farmaya hai. aur qaza' se murad ye hai ke bachchey ke sar se kuchh baal moond diye jaeyn aur kuchh chhod diye jaeyn.
4194,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ''qaza' '' se mana farmaya hai aur wo ye hai ke bachchey ka sara sar moond diya jaey aur koi eik lat baqi rakhi jaey.
4195,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik bachchey ko dekha ke uskey kuchh baal moond diye gaey they aur kuchh chhodey huey they to aapney unhen is se mana farmaya aur kaha : ''uskey sarey baal moond do ya sarey rakho.''
4196,"Saiyedna Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke meri lambi-lambi zulfein thin. meri walida ne mujh se kaha : unhen mat kaato , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) inhen (piyaar sey) khinchtey they aur pakad liya kartey they."
4197,Hajjaj bin Hassaan ne bayan kiya ke ham Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey. meri behan Mughira ne bayan kiya ke tum un dino nau-umr bachchey they aur tumharey baalon ki do laten thin. to unhoney tumharey sar par haath phera aur tumharey liye barkat ki dua ki aur farmaya : inhen moond dalo ya katarwaa lo. bila-shuba ye yahudiyon ki alamat hai.
4198,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain : ''fitri umur (baaten) paanch hain, ya farmaya ke paanch baaten fitrat se hain : khatna karana , zere naaf ki safai , baghlon ke baal ukhedna , nakhun tarashna aur moonchhen kutarwana.''"
4199,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai : bila-shuba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne moonchhen mundwaane aur daadhiyaan badhaney ka hukm diya hai.
4200,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne riwayat kiya, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamarey liye had muqarrar kar di thi ke zere-naaf ki safai, nakhun taraashney, moonchhen kaatney aur baghlon ke baal ukhedney ka amal chaalis din main eik baar (zarur) kar liya jaey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is riwayat ko Jaafar bin Sulaiman ne ba-waaste Abu-Imraan Hazrat Anas se riwayat kiya, magar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka zikr nahin kiya. aur kaha : ''hamarey liye ye had muqarrar ki gaee thi.'' aur ye ziyada sahih hai. (aur Sadqa Daqeeqi qawi (mazboot) raawi nahin hai)"
4201,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham log hajj aur Umerey ke alawa daadhiyon ko chhode rakhtey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke (الاستحداد) ka mafhoom zere-naaf (naabhi ke neeche ke) baalon ki safai hai.
4202,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' safed baal mat nocha karo, jis kisi musalman ke baal haalate-Islam mein safed ho jaeyn qiyamat ke din ye uskey liye Noor ka baais hongey.'' aur Yahya ki riwayat mein hai. ''Allah taala eik eik baal ke iwaz uski neki likhtaa hai aur eik gunah door karta hai.''"
4203,Saiyedna Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''yahudi aur Esaee apney baalon ko nahin rangtey isliye tum unki mukhalifat kiya karo.'' (yani rangaa karo .)
4204,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Fateh Makka ke roz (Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke walid) Abu-Qahaafa ko laya gaya to unke sar aur dadhi ke baal saghma buti ki manind safed they to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''inhen kisi rang se badal do aur siyahi se bacho.''
4205,Saiyedna Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tehqiq sab se behtar cheez jis se ye safed baal rangey jatey hain mehndi aur katam hai.''
4206,"Hazrat Abu-Ramsa (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke main apney walid ke sath Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua maine dekha ke aap ke baal kanon tak they, un mein mehndi ke rang ki jhalak thi aur aap do sabz (hari) chadaren audhey huey they."
4207,"Yaad bin Laqeet ne Hazrat Abu-Ramsa (Raziallahu anhu) se ye hadees bayan ki, unhoney kaha ke merey walid ne aap se arz kiya : ye jo aap ki kamar par hai mujhey dikhayen , main Tabeeb (Muaalij) hun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tabeeb tu Allah hai, tum rafeeq (tasalli deney waley aur narmi karney waley) ho. tabeeb wo hai jisney usey paida kiya hai.''"
4208,Hazrat Abu-Ramsa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke main aur merey walid Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye. aapney eik shakhs se ya merey walid se (merey mutalliq poochha) ke ''ye kon hai?'' unhoney kaha : ye mera beta hai. aapney farmaya : ''ye tera qusur nahin uthaey ga.'' (yani har shakhs apney aamaal ka khud zimmedar aur jawaab-deh hai.) aur aapney apni dadhi mehndi se rangi hui thi.
4209,Saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke khizaab ke baarey mein sawal kiya gaya to unhoney bataya ke aapney apney baal nahin rangey. lekin Abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne rangey hain.
4210,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sabti (rangi hui khaal se baney huey) jootey istimal kiya kartey they aur apni dadhi ko waras aur Zaafran bhi lagatey they. chunanche Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bhi yehi amal tha.
4211,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se eik aadmi ka guzar hua jisney apney baal mehndi se rangey huey they to aapney farmaya : ''ye kya khoob hai ! '' phir doosra aadmi guzra jisney mehndi aur katam (buti) se rangey huey they. aapney farmaya : ''ye us se badh kar umda hai.'' phir eik aur guzra, jisney zard rang se rangey huey they, aapney farmaya : ''ye un sab se umda hai.''"
4212,"Saiyedna ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aakhir zamaney mein aisey log hongey jo siyah rang se apney baal rangeen gey jaisey kabootron ke seeney hotey hain, ye log jannat ki khushbu nahin paeyn gey.''"
4213,"Saiyedna Soban maula Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab safar ke liye rawana hotey to apney ehle ke jis fard se sab se aakhir mein mulaqat kartey wo Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) hotin. aur jab wapis aatey to sab se pehley Sayeda Fatima hi ke yahan tashrif latey. aap apney eik ghazwe se wapis aaye jabkey Sayeda Fatima ne apney darwazey par taat ya parda latkaayaa hua tha aur Hazrat Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko chaandi ke kangan pahnaaey huey they. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye magar andar nahin gaey. to Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko guman hua ke aap ke andar na aaney ka sabab yehi hai jo unhoney dekha hai. chunanche unhoney parda phaad diya aur bachchon se kangan utaar liye aur unke samney hi unhen tod dala to wo rotey huey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas chaley gaey. aapney un dono se wo ley liye aur farmaya : ''aey Soban ! inhen falan ghar walon ke paas ley jao . ''jo ehale-Madina mein se they. aapney farmaya : ''ye log (Fatima, Ali, Hasan, Husain (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum)) merey ehale-bait hain, mujhey ye baat pasand nahin ke ye apni nekiyon ki jaza isi duniya mein kha lein. aey Soban ! Fatima ke liye asab (mankon) ka eik haar aur haathi daant ke do kangan kharid lana.''"
